Thanks to its excellent performance and outstanding workmanship, it has a stellar reputation and has been widely used in multiple fields, including outdoor activities, military use, law enforcement, industrial lighting, aviation, marine, etc. In some areas, JETBeam has been regarded as one of the leading mid-to-high end flashlight brands and flashlight technology development explorers. Its body crafted from sturdy titanium alloy and plated with 24K gold, the Jetbeam TEA30 is the perfect collectors item for any flashlight enthusiast. Its unique body is both durable and watertight, able to be submerged under 2 meters of water without any damage to the flashlight. The TEA30 runs on a single AAA battery and uses its CREE XP-G LED to produce up to 131 Lumens of light that can reach up to 37 meters away. The flashlight also features 2 lower brightness settings of 34 Lumens and 6 Lumens, all of which can be accessed and cycled through using the easy-to-use tail cap switch. Just over three inches in length and complete with a metal pocket clip, this eye-catching flashlight is an easy carry for any everyday user.Jetbeam Tea30 Limited Edition Titanium/Gold Plated
